file.name: extendedItem.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Example API
paths:
  '/v1/resource':
    get:
      operationId: getResources
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ExtendedItem'
components:
  schemas:
    ExtendedItem:
      allOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/ParentObject'
        - type: object
          properties:
            mandatoryChildInteger:
              type: integer
            optionalChildString:
              type: string
          required:
            - mandatoryChildInteger
    ParentObject:
      type: object
      properties:
        madatoryParentString:
          type: string
        optionalParentInteger:
          type: integer
      required:
        - madatoryParentString
